usage: __main__.py [-h] [-r TIMES] [-p] [-s NUM_VERTEXES] [-d DEGREE]
                   [-m {dfs,quick}]
                   f

Program To Try Four-colors-Theorom

positional arguments:
  f                     The dir you wanna figures to be stored

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -r TIMES, --repeat TIMES
                        $times you wanna repeat.Default=20
  -p                    Print the Graph_structure on the standard out(You can
                        use">" to redirect it
  -s NUM_VERTEXES, --size NUM_VERTEXES
                        The number of vertexes in the graph, deault=10
  -d DEGREE, --degree DEGREE
                        The max number of degrees per vertexes holds,
                        default=10
  -m {dfs,quick}, --mod {dfs,quick}
                        The Paint Mode You Prefer:[dfs, dff, quick]
